                        <span>‚úì</span> <span id="complianceText">C√≥digo v√°lido seg√∫n est√°ndares internacionales</span>
                    </div>
                    
                    <div id="nonComplianceInfo" class="gs1-non-compliance" style="display: none;">
                        <span>‚úó</span> <span id="nonComplianceText">Error en el c√≥digo</span>
